text: Hillsborough County is a county in the U.S. state of Florida, and was formed on June 13, 1915. As of 2020, 1,459,762 people lived there. Hillsborough County's seat is Tampa. ==References== ==Other websites== *Official county website Category:Florida counties Category:1834 establishments in the United States Category:1830s establishments in Florida Territory
